name: Surreal Oneiromancy Dream #1
description:
Surreal oneiromancy will group occult dream-like paintings of omens and visions, bringing the dark magical realm manifesting in dreams into art.

I feel like putting a description on this would defy the purpose of the collection. I would like to let you as the viewer, use your own imagination to fill in the gaps, and make up your own story about each one of these dream-like paintings. The goal is to allow you to create your own interpretations, without me influencing them.
